
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<!-- CSS stilini burada yazıyoruz -->
<style>
    body {
        background-color: black;
        color: white;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .content {
        max-width: 80%;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin: 10px 0;
    }

    a {
        color: #1DB954;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
</style>

<div class="content">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
        Your privacy is important to us. This page outlines how we handle your data and protect your personal information while using our application.
    </p>
    <p>
        - We do not collect or share any personal data without your consent.<br>
        - All interactions with the application are secure and private.<br>
        - Data used for mood analysis is processed locally and not shared with third parties.
    </p>
    <p>
        For more detailed information about our privacy practices, please contact us at <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">your-email@example.com</a>.
    </p>
</div>
